<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>UDA – United Doctors Association, Pune</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav id="navbar">
  <%= link_to root_path, data: { turbo: false }, class: "nav-logo" do %>
    <div class="logo-icon">✚</div>
    <div class="logo-text">
      <span class="main">UDA</span>
      <span class="sub">Pune, India</span>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><%= link_to "Home", root_path, data: { turbo: false } %></li>
    <li><a href="#about" data-turbo="false">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#leadership" data-turbo="false">Leadership</a></li>
    <li><a href="#activities" data-turbo="false">Activities</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact" data-turbo="false">Contact</a></li>
    <li><a href="/members" data-turbo="false">Members</a></li>
    <li><%= link_to "JOIN UDA", new_registration_path  %></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section id="home">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-grid"></div>
  <div class="hero-cross">✚</div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">Established · Pune, Maharashtra · 2001</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title"><span class="uda">UDA</span></h1>
    <div class="hero-full-name">United Doctors Association</div>
    <div class="hero-divider"></div>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Uniting Medical Minds. Advancing Healthcare.<br/>Serving the People of Pune.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <%= link_to "JOIN UDA TODAY", new_registration_path, class: "btn-outline"  %>
      <a href="#about" data-turbo="false" class="btn-outline">Discover More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num" data-target="600">0</div><div class="stat-label">Members</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num" data-target="23">0</div><div class="stat-label">Years Active</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num" data-target="120">0</div><div class="stat-label">Events Held</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num" data-target="50000">0</div><div class="stat-label">Lives Touched</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── ABOUT ── -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <div class="section-tag">Who We Are</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Championing the Future of Medicine in Pune</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <p>The United Doctors Association (UDA) is Pune's premier medical fraternity, founded to bridge the gap between medical professionals and the community. Since 2001, we have united doctors across all specializations under a single, powerful banner of service.</p>
      <p>UDA serves as the collective voice of Pune's medical community—advocating for healthcare policy reforms, organizing continuing medical education, and spearheading community health initiatives across the city and surrounding districts.</p>
      <p>Our members represent the finest physicians, surgeons, and specialists dedicated not just to their patients, but to elevating the entire standard of healthcare in Maharashtra.</p>
      <div class="about-features">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">🏥</div>
          <div class="feature-title">Healthcare Advocacy</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Representing doctors at policy levels across Maharashtra</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">🎓</div>
          <div class="feature-title">CME Programs</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Regular continuing medical education seminars & workshops</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
          <div class="feature-title">Community Service</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Free health camps and social welfare initiatives citywide</div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <div class="feature-icon">⚖️</div>
          <div class="feature-title">Legal Support</div>
          <div class="feature-desc">Medico-legal guidance and protection for member doctors</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual reveal">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="mission-item">
          <div class="mission-label">Our Mission</div>
          <div class="mission-text">"To unite, empower, and support every doctor in Pune — fostering excellence in medicine and compassion in care."</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-item">
          <div class="mission-label">Our Vision</div>
          <div class="mission-text">"A Pune where world-class healthcare is accessible to all, delivered by a unified, empowered medical community."</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-label" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Core Values</div>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-chip">⚕ Integrity</div>
          <div class="value-chip">💡 Innovation</div>
          <div class="value-chip">🌿 Compassion</div>
          <div class="value-chip">🤝 Unity</div>
          <div class="value-chip">📚 Education</div>
          <div class="value-chip">🛡 Ethics</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── LEADERSHIP ── -->
<section id="leadership">
  <div class="leadership-inner">
    <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="section-tag" style="justify-content:center;">Our Leadership</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Guiding Hands of UDA</h2>
      <div class="gold-line" style="margin:20px auto;"></div>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin:0 auto;">Our elected leadership comprises distinguished physicians who have dedicated their careers to both medicine and the advancement of our medical community.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="leaders-grid">
        <!-- President -->
        <div class="leader-card featured reveal">
            <div class="leader-photo-wrap">
            <div class="leader-photo-ring-outer">
                <%= image_tag "Dr_Munaf_Inamdar.jpeg", class: "leader-img", alt: "Dr. Munaf Inamdar" %>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="leader-role-badge">✦ President</div>
            <div class="leader-name">Dr. Munaf Inamdar</div>
            <div class="leader-qual">MBBS · MD</div>
            <p class="leader-bio">A distinguished physician with years of clinical and administrative experience. Under his visionary leadership, UDA has grown to become one of Maharashtra's most respected medical associations.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vice President -->
        <div class="leader-card featured reveal">
            <div class="leader-photo-wrap">
            <div class="leader-photo-ring-outer">
                <%= image_tag "Dr_Attar.jpeg", class: "leader-img", alt: "Dr. Zakir Attar" %>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="leader-role-badge">✦ Vice President</div>
            <div class="leader-name">Dr. Zakir Attar</div>
            <div class="leader-qual">BHMS</div>
            <p class="leader-bio">A renowned physician and health advocate. He has been instrumental in establishing UDA's community outreach programs and strengthening the association's ties with Pune's medical institutions.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Secretary -->
        <div class="leader-card featured reveal">
            <div class="leader-photo-wrap">
            <div class="leader-photo-ring-outer">
                <%= image_tag "Dr_Ausaf .jpeg", class: "leader-img", alt: "Dr. Ausaf Shaikh" %>
            </div>
            </div>
            <div class="leader-role-badge">✦ Secretary</div>
            <div class="leader-name">Dr. Ausaf Shaikh</div>
            <div class="leader-qual">BAMS · LLB</div>
            <p class="leader-bio">Manages UDA's day-to-day operations with remarkable efficiency. He oversees member relations, event coordination, and has been a key figure in UDA's legal advocacy and community service initiatives.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ── ACTIVITIES ── -->
<section id="activities">
  <div class="activities-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-tag">What We Do</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Work & Past Activities</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <p class="section-subtitle">From life-saving health camps to landmark medical conferences, UDA has been at the forefront of community healthcare for over two decades.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="activities-grid">
      <div class="activity-card act-1 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">🏕️</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">March 2024</div>
          <div class="activity-title">Annual Free Health Camp</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">Over 2,000 underprivileged citizens received free consultations, blood tests, and medicines at our flagship health camp held at Shivajinagar Grounds.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Community Health</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-card act-2 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">🩸</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">January 2024</div>
          <div class="activity-title">Blood Donation Drive</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">UDA organized Pune's largest single-day blood donation event, collecting 800+ units in collaboration with Ruby Hall Clinic and KEM Hospital.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Donation Drive</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-card act-3 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">🎓</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">November 2023</div>
          <div class="activity-title">CME National Conference</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">Three-day Continuing Medical Education conference on advances in oncology and cardiology. Over 400 doctors from 12 states participated.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Medical Education</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-card act-4 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">🦠</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">2020 – 2022</div>
          <div class="activity-title">COVID-19 Relief Operations</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">UDA mobilized 300+ volunteer doctors, set up oxygen banks, and coordinated emergency medical response during the pandemic's peak in Pune.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Emergency Relief</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-card act-5 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">👁️</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">September 2023</div>
          <div class="activity-title">Free Eye Checkup Camp</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">In partnership with Drishti Foundation, UDA screened 1,500 patients for cataracts and diabetic retinopathy, providing free spectacles to 300 seniors.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Preventive Health</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="activity-card act-6 reveal">
        <div class="activity-img">🚶</div>
        <div class="activity-body">
          <div class="activity-date">April 2023</div>
          <div class="activity-title">Medical Awareness Marathon</div>
          <p class="activity-desc">UDA's annual walkathon drew 5,000 participants across Pune to raise awareness about diabetes, hypertension, and cancer prevention.</p>
          <span class="activity-tag">Public Awareness</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<!-- ── CONTACT & FOOTER ── -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="contact-grid reveal">
    <div class="contact-brand">
      <div class="logo-big">UDA</div>
      <div class="logo-sub">United Doctors Association · Pune</div>
      <p>Dedicated to the health and wellbeing of the people of Pune. A trusted medical fraternity since 2001, uniting over 600 doctors across all specializations.</p>
      <div class="social-row">
        <div class="social-btn" title="Facebook">🇫</div>
        <div class="social-btn" title="Instagram">📸</div>
        <div class="social-btn" title="Twitter/X">✖</div>
        <div class="social-btn" title="LinkedIn">💼</div>
        <div class="social-btn" title="YouTube">▶</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-col">
      <h4>Quick Links</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "Home", root_path %></li>
        <li><a href="#about">About UDA</a></li>
        <li><a href="#leadership">Our Leadership</a></li>
        <li><a href="#activities">Past Activities</a></li>
        <li><%= link_to "JOIN UDA", new_registration_path  %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-col">
      <h4>Contact Us</h4>
      <div class="contact-info-item">
        <div class="ci-icon">📍</div>
        <div class="ci-text">UDA House, [Address],<br/>Pune – 411001, Maharashtra</div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-info-item">
        <div class="ci-icon">📞</div>
        <div class="ci-text">+91 20 XXXX XXXX<br/>+91 98XXXXXXXX</div>
      </div>
      <div class="contact-info-item">
        <div class="ci-icon">✉️</div>
        <div class="ci-text">info@udapune.org<br/>membership@udapune.org</div>
